ASoC: rsnd: add rsnd_ssi_busif_err_irq_enable/disable()

Current ssi.c has duplicated code to control BUSIF
over/under run interrupt.
This patch adds new rsnd_ssi_busif_err_irq_enable/disable()
and share the code.

